rows.label: qst650205_0010
rows.name: Everyone. Sorry to keep friends waiting.

rows.label: qst650205_0020
rows.name:
Hana...
What in Alst Grampypon Senzo do...?

rows.label: qst650205_0060
rows.name:
Negative. This Hana is Hana Mk. II.
Is great honor to meet friends of Professor.

rows.label: qst650205_0070
rows.name: Huh? He's made a second Hana?!

rows.label: qst650205_0100
rows.name:
Hana Mk. II operate under
remote control of Hana.

rows.label: qst650205_0110
rows.name:
Exactly.
Hana Mk. II have no will of her own.

rows.label: qst650205_0120
rows.name:
Hana do steering, and play Hana voice
through clever speaker system.

rows.label: qst650205_0130
rows.name:
This function open world of possibility, like fresh
new improv routine where Hana play off of Hana.

rows.label: qst650205_0150
rows.name:
That sounds fascinating...
But perhaps best left for another time.

rows.label: qst650205_0160
rows.name:
So Grampypon want Boss and friends
to also have Hana they can use...

rows.label: qst650205_0170
rows.name: and that why make Hana Mk. II?

rows.label: qst650205_0180
rows.name:
Wow... We'd be pretty unstoppable
with another Hana by our side!

rows.label: qst650205_0200
rows.name:
Friends still thinking small,
like Tasty Sausage for littlepon!

rows.label: qst650205_0210
rows.name: Senzo not have time to dream small!

rows.label: qst650205_0270
rows.name: Why is it shaped...like a Nopon?

rows.label: qst650205_0290
rows.name:
Thank you kindly for your compliment.
You, too, are exceedingly cute.

rows.label: qst650205_0310
rows.name:
Senzo equip it with specially-crafted artificial intelligence
program! Is made to support Hana.

rows.label: qst650205_0320
rows.name:
Yes. I am indeed, if you pardon the self-aggrandizement,
a superlative AI. Your awe is fully warranted.

rows.label: qst650205_0340
rows.name: Oho, this is only tippedy-tip of iceberg...

rows.label: qst650205_0430
rows.name:
Valued friends of Hana-san. The Hanabuster is
standing by to excel, pending your orders.
